<h4>Curling league&nbsp;</h4>
<ul>
<li>Beginner mixed league (ages 18+)&nbsp;</li>
<li><a href="mailto:SportsplexAthletics@ottawa.ca" target="_blank">SportsplexAthletics@ottawa.ca</a>&nbsp;for additional information.</li>
</ul>
<h4>Book a bonspiel (rental)</h4>
<ul>
<li>Set up a bonspiel for team building with your friends or work colleagues. </li>
<li>If you are interested in additional catering options, please fill out the <a href="https://www.tulipsandmaple.ca/ottawa/contact-us/" target="_blank">online request form for Tulips and Maple Catering</a>.&nbsp;</li>
<li>For ice rental information and availability, please email <a href="mailto:SportsplexAthletics@ottawa.ca" target="_blank">SportsplexAthletics@ottawa.ca</a>.</li>
</ul>
<h4>Bar/lounge and boardroom</h4>
<p>These hours are subject to change.</p>
<ul>
<li>Monday, 6:30 to 10:30 pm&nbsp;</li>
<li>Tuesday, 4:30 to 10:30 pm&nbsp;</li>
